        <inline name="agenda item name">General and complete disarmament: confidence-building measures in the regional and subregional context</inline>
      </p>
      <p>
        <docTitle>Resolution adopted by the General Assembly on 6 December 2021</docTitle>
      </p>
      <p xml:space="preserve">
